===Particle===
[[Category:Japanese particles]]
'''を''' (o)

# grammatical marker for the direct object of a verb.
#:When used in this sense it is almost always pronounced "o"

====Translations====
*Hebrew: [[את]]
*Korean: [[을]] (eul) (''follows consonants''), [[를]] (reul) (''follows vowels'')
*Spanish: [[a]] (only used when the object is a person)


